e made him seem a very human character."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Thomas Ainsworth was born in 1590, in Frodsham, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom, his father, Henrie Ainsworth, was 23 and his mother, Jean Harwood, was 32. He married Jane Rothwell on 13 July 1612. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1659, in Lancashire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 69."},"et":{"1590–1659":"1590–1659","1596–Female":"1596–Surnud","1590–1645":"1590–1645","1612–1704":"1612–1704","1567–1615":"1567–1615","1558–Female":"1558–Surnud","13 Jul 1612":"13. juuli 1612","29 Mar 1615":"29. märts 1615","1590":"1590","1558":"1558","1612":"1612","1645":"1645","1567":"1567","1596":"1596","about 1645":"umbes 1645","30 Oct 1589":"30. oktoober 1589","1704":"1704","1659":"1659","1615":"1615","Frodsham, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Frodsham, Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Frodsham, Cheshire, England":"Frodsham, Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Dean by Burnley, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Dean by Burnley, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","St Bartholomew, Great Harwood, Lancashire, England":"Harwood, Lancashire, England"},"fi":{"1590–1659":"1590–1659","1596–Female":"1596–Kuollut","1590–1645":"1590–1645","1612–1704":"1612–1704","1567–1615":"1567–1615","1558–Female":"1558–Kuollut","13 Jul 1612":"13. heinäkuuta 1612","29 Mar 1615":"29. maaliskuuta 1615","1590":"1590","1558":"1558","1612":"1612","1645":"1645","1567":"1567","1596":"1596","about 1645":"noin 1645","30 Oct 1589":"30. lokakuuta 1589","1704":"1704","1659":"1659","1615":"1615","Frodsham, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Frodsham, Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Frodsham, Cheshire, England":"Frodsham, Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Lancashire, Englan